      "text": "Twinkling."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.72,
      "end": 69.82,
      "text": "Yeah, 난리나세요, 난리나요."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.1,
      "end": 72.58,
      "text": "Yeah, many people think I'm a 딸 바보"
    },
