    {
      "start": 229.22,
      "end": 229.48,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.62,
      "end": 231.04,
      "text": "일단 그런 거 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.24,
      "end": 234.52,
      "text": "Sometimes it takes a lot of time to be recognized, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.68,
      "end": 235.72,
      "text": "Yeah, it's not easy."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.76,
      "end": 236.36,
      "text": "It requires patience."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.6,
      "end": 239.24,
      "text": "Patience and try and try again."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.84,
      "end": 244.0,
      "text": "Luckily, he had someone who recognized his talent and put on the play again."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.16,
      "end": 244.64,
      "text": "Exactly."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.98,
      "end": 249.8,
      "text": "The audience, they wanted something easy to understand, something easy to laugh at."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.8,
      "end": 254.12,
      "text": "But this play was kind of difficult, and they did not like it at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.12,
      "end": 261.62,
      "text": "어쨌든, 조케의 트위스트를 결과적으로 이끌 수가 있어서 너무 다행이다라는 생각이 듭니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.8,
      "end": 262.04,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.18,
      "end": 266.4,
      "text": "He has three other big plays that he wrote after this one."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.9,
      "end": 270.08,
      "text": "Uncle Vanya, Three Sisters, and The Cherry Orchard."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.08,
      "end": 272.82,
      "text": "So he didn't give up at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.88,
      "end": 273.28,
      "text": "He didn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.34,
      "end": 277.3,
      "text": "He went on to become the famous successful playwright."
    },
    {
      "start": 277.54,
      "end": 279.1,
      "text": "너무 다행입니다, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.22,
      "end": 279.4,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.52,
      "end": 281.74,
      "text": "오늘 준비된 장면 먼저 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.08,
      "end": 284.52,
      "text": "When people have nothing better to say, they say, youth."
